  syl(wal(s0, wceq(cv(s0), cv(s1))), wal(s9, wi(wceq(cv(s10), cv(s11)), wceq(cv(s12), cv(s13)))), wal(hs0, wceq(cv(hs0), cv(hs1))))
  aev(s0, s1, hs0, hs0, hs1)
  alrimiv(s9, wal(hs0, wceq(cv(hs0), cv(hs1))), wi(wceq(cv(s10), cv(s11)), wceq(cv(s12), cv(s13))))
  a1d(wal(hs0, wceq(cv(hs0), cv(hs1))), wceq(cv(s10), cv(s11)), wceq(cv(s12), cv(s13)))
  aeveq(hs0, hs1, s12, s13)
  diff.wal.s(s9, hs0, wceq(cv(hs0), cv(hs1)))
  diff.wceq.s(s9, cv(hs0), cv(hs1))
  diff.cv.s(s9, hs0)

  diff.hs1.s(s9)
  diff.hs0.s(hs1)
}
